					title: "<p class='ql-align-left'><span class='ql-font-serif'>ZDF系列单效纤维分离机/ ZDF Series Fiber Separator</span></p>",
					nameFn: '',
					past: "<p><span>ZDF系列单效纤维分离机/ ZDF Series Fiber Separator</span></p><p>用 途 ：</p><p>纤维分离机是一种利用纤维比重差而除掉废纸原料中的各种杂质，具有疏解、分离和粗筛选组合作用。一般装置在水力碎浆机后作为二级碎浆、分离设备。也可作为尾渣的处理设备。</p><p>结构特点：</p><p>具有浆料的二级疏解，轻杂质分离，重、粗废料的清除三种基本功能。可以使用低级的废纸，减少原料的预处理。</p><p>可以提高现有水力碎浆机的生产能力，可以节约10~20%的单位消耗能量。可以获得优质的浆料，纤维损失小，提高筛选的效率。</p><p>Design Features</p><p>Three fundamental functions: secondary defibering, separating light impurities, removing heavy and coarse impurities.</p><p>With the defibrater in the pulping process,fiber separator uses the recycled paper with poor quality and reduces the pretreatment of the raw material.</p><p>Fiber separator increases the production of existing hydrapulper, reduces the energy consumption by 10~20%. Fiber separator obtains high quality stock,reduces fiber loss and increases screening efficiency.</p><p>Application:</p><p>Fiber separator can remove all kinds of impurities of recycled paper with help of the different specific gravity of fibers. It com- bines</p><p>the functions of defibering, separating and screening in one unit. As a secondary pulping and separating equipment, it is normally adownsteam equipment of the hydrapulper. As a reject screen, fiber separator can also handle with coarse impurities.</p>",
