					nameFn: '',
					past: "<p>ZDN系列带式污泥压滤机/ ZDN Series Belt Type Sludge Press</p><p>用 途:</p><p>污泥挤压机是国际上通用的挤压机械，其应用范围很广，如造纸环保污水、市政污水、矿山污水、印漂染污水、化纤污水等行业都可用其使液固分离。</p><p>结构特点:</p><p>带式浓缩压滤机处理进浆浓度在1-3%以上的污泥，温度应在20C左右. 通过多道脱水环节，如重力脱水、回旋脱水和剪切脱水等处理，使污泥达到15%以上的干度.</p><p>Application:</p><p>Sludge press is the press equipment, widely used for paper mill sewage, municipal sewage, mineral waste water, bleaching &amp; dyeing sewage, chemical fiber sewage etc. To separate the water.</p><p>Design Features:</p><p>It is to process sludge with 1-3% inlet consistency and feeding temperatue of about 20'C. Sludge will reach 15% or higher consis- tency through various dewatering procedure，including gravit dewatering，wedge dewatering，swing dewatering，shear dewatering.</p><p>Belt-type thickener is widely applied in sludge handling system. It is tum sludge with low consistency to higher consistency。</p>",
