					nameFn: '',
					past: "<p>ZDS系列D型水力碎浆机/ ZDS Series D-type Hydrapulper</p><p><br></p><p><strong>结构特点:</strong></p><p>适用于OCC、商品废纸等的间歇或连续碎解，采用D型槽体，改变了传统碎浆机产生的涡流形式，增加碎浆机中浆流的湍动和涡流方向，使纸捆快速浸入液面以下，以改进废纸原料 在碎浆机中的移动路径来提高碎浆机生产能力。可缩短碎解时间 ，降低能耗，提高单位容积的生产能力。</p><p><strong>Design Features:</strong></p><p>D-type Hydrapulper is more suitable for pulping OCC, commercial waste paper continually or in batch. With D-shaped vat, in the way of generating turbulence in the conventional pulper has been changed, the turbulence is intensified and so the paper bale is quickly soaked into the liquid, in this way the moving path of waste paper in pulper is improved and the capacity of pulper increases. It can shorten the pulping time, reduce energy consumption and increase the specific capac- ity per unit of volume.</p>",
